🟦 1. General Platform Questions
What is Grains Hub? — Grains Hub is Dubai’s verified B2B grain trading platform offering stock, FCL booking, supplier verification, and market intelligence.

How does Grains Hub work? — Buyers browse stock, verify suppliers, book FCL shipments, and access Market Pulse for live pricing.

Is Grains Hub verified? — Yes, verified by Cisco Talos, Norton, and Sucuri with full SPF/DKIM/DMARC compliance.

Where is Grains Hub located? — Dubai, UAE.

How do I contact Grains Hub? — WhatsApp +971 58 552 1976 or FCL booking page.

🟦 2. Buyer Questions
How do I buy rice? — Browse stock at grains.ae/shop or submit an FCL booking.

Do you have 1121 Sella? — Yes, check live stock at grains.ae/shop.

Do you have Irri 6? — Yes, available in both AED stock and USD booking.

Can I buy small quantities? — Yes, AED stock is available for local buyers.

Can I buy full container loads? — Yes, book via grains.ae/fcl.

🟦 3. Supplier Questions
How do I onboard as a supplier? — Submit your company profile, product list, and verification documents. Download supplier pack.

How do I get verified? — Verification requires compliance documents, trade history, and product samples.

How do I list my products? — After verification, your products appear in stock.json and supplier directory.

Can I update my supplier profile? — Yes, contact Grains Hub support.

🟦 4. FCL Booking Questions
How do I book an FCL shipment? — Use grains.ae/fcl for instant booking and email confirmation.

What origins are available? — India, Pakistan, Thailand.

Do you support 20ft and 40ft? — Yes, both container sizes.

How long does booking confirmation take? — Instant via Firebase backend.

🟦 5. Market Pulse & Pricing Questions
What is Market Pulse? — A Bloomberg-style live price dashboard updated every 60 seconds.

What is the price of 1121 Sella? — Check live price at grains.ae/pulse/test.

What is the price of Irri 6? — Check live price at grains.ae/pulse/test.

Is the market up or down? — Market Pulse shows trend arrows and mood percentage.

Where can I see market analysis? — Download market analysis report.

